graph LR
    RHODSOperator[RHODS Operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    RHODSOperator -->|requires| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.26+<br/>Core Platform]
    RHODSOperator -->|requires| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.11+<br/>Routes, OAuth, SCC]
    RHODSOperator -->|uses| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.14.6<br/>K8s Controller Framework]

    %% External Dependencies - Conditional
    RHODSOperator -->|conditional| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Operator<br/>Istio - mTLS, AuthZ]
    RHODSOperator -->|conditional| Serverless[Serverless Operator<br/>Knative Serving]
    RHODSOperator -->|conditional| Authorino[Authorino Operator<br/>External Authorization]
    RHODSOperator -->|conditional| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    RHODSOperator -.->|optional| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.68.0<br/>Monitoring]
    RHODSOperator -.->|optional| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Certificate Mgmt]

    %% External Services
    RHODSOperator -->|fetches manifests| GitHub[GitHub<br/>Component Manifests]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Components - Managed
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| KServe[KServe<br/>Serverless Model Serving]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Multi-Model Serving]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| DSP[Data Science Pipelines<br/>ML Workflows]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Jupyter, VS Code]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| CodeFlare[CodeFlare<br/>Distributed Training]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| Ray[Ray<br/>Distributed Computing]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job Queueing]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| TrainingOp[Training Operator<br/>PyTorch, TF, XGBoost]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>Explainability]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|integrates| RHODSOperator
    DSP -->|integrates| RHODSOperator

    %% Component Dependencies
    KServe -->|requires| ServiceMesh
    KServe -->|requires| Serverless
    KServe -.->|optional| CertManager

    DSP -->|requires| Tekton

    ServiceMesh -->|uses| Authorino

    %% API Server
    RHODSOperator -->|manages resources| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]

